Rounded Rectangle
Name: BTN_ADD_or_DEL_DV
Text: Agregar
Bold: msoTrue
Font Size: 10
Font Color: White
Fill Color: RGB(25, 107, 36)
Line Color: RGB(25, 107, 36)
Other: msoAnchorMiddle and msoAlignCenter

**** IF I4 IS "Agregar" AND I6 IS "Categoría" THEN 
- FOR SHAPE LOCATED IN H10 SET .OnAction = Add_Category

**** IF I4 IS "Agregar" AND I6 IS "De" THEN 
- FOR SHAPE LOCATED IN H10 SET .OnAction = Add_De

**** IF I4 IS "Eliminar" THEN: 
- SET H6 CONTENT TO "De" WITHOUT CHANGING ANY FORMAT. 
- CLEAR I6 CONTENT WITHOUT REMOVING DATA VALIDATION. 
- CLEAR I8 CONTENT AND REMOVE ANY DATA VALIDATION FROM IT. 
- REMOVE ANY SHAPE BUTTON LOCATED IN CELL H10. 
- CREATE SHAPE BUTTON IN CELL H10 WITH THE FOLLOWING DETAILS: 
Rounded Rectangle
