Text: Eliminar
Bold: msoTrue
Font Size: 10
Font Color: White
Fill Color: RGB(192, 0, 0)
Line Color: RGB(192, 0, 0)
Other: msoAnchorMiddle and msoAlignCenter

**** IF I4 IS "Eliminar" AND I6 IS "Categoría" THEN: 
- APPLY DATA VALIDATION DROPDOWN LIST TO CELL I8. 
- THE DROPDOWN MUST CONTAIN THE DATA BODY OF TABLE "DATA_BANK_CATEGORY".
- FOR SHAPE LOCATED IN H10 SET .OnAction = Del_Category

**** IF I4 IS "Eliminar" AND I6 IS "De" THEN: 
- APPLY DATA VALIDATION DROPDOWN LIST TO CELL I8. 
- THE DROPDOWN MUST CONTAIN THE DATA BODY OF TABLE "DATA_BANK_DE".
- FOR SHAPE LOCATED IN H10 SET .OnAction = Del_De 

**** IF I4 GETS CLEARED THEN: 
- CLEAR I6 AND I8. 
- REMOVE ANY DATA VALIDATION LOCATED IN CELL I8. 

**** IF I6 GETS CLEARED THEN:
- CLEAR I8. 
- REMOVE ANY DATA VALIDATION LOCATED IN CELL I8. 



